  "detailed_description": "Space tower, where the player controls a neat spherical CPU. <br>The tower is full of various crises. In addition to the need to avoid falling from high places under normal gravity, area attacks of different types of damage such as lightning strikes, fire and freezing will appear. As the story progresses, you will experience low-gravity or even zero-gravity space, and the difficulty of control often overturns your feel that victory is inevitable.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279640/extras/3836e1472692aa00997618232ee2a24f.poster.avif?t=1690283244\" width=720 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279640/extras/3836e1472692aa00997618232ee2a24f.webm?t=1690283244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279640/extras/3836e1472692aa00997618232ee2a24f.mp4?t=1690283244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Move in the water with buoyancy<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279640/extras/b4e815c20f42317c4a7db45742aba50c.poster.avif?t=1690283244\" width=720 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279640/extras/b4e815c20f42317c4a7db45742aba50c.webm?t=1690283244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279640/extras/b4e815c20f42317c4a7db45742aba50c.mp4?t=1690283244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Activities in low gravity without impact damage<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279640/